  "prompt": "What is the healthiest food I can snack on throughout the day? Must be fairly affordable + fairly tasty.",
  "response": "There are several healthy, affordable, and tasty snacks you can enjoy throughout the day. Here are some great options:\n\n1. **Fresh Fruits**: Apples, bananas, oranges, and berries are all nutritious, portable, and generally inexpensive. They provide vitamins, fiber, and natural sweetness.\n\n2. **Vegetable Sticks with Hummus**: Carrot sticks, cucumber slices, or bell pepper strips paired with hummus make for a crunchy, satisfying snack that\u2019s rich in fiber and protein.\n\n3. **Greek Yogurt**: A single-serving container of plain Greek yogurt is high in protein and can be enjoyed plain or with a sprinkle of fruit, nuts, or honey for added flavor.\n\n4. **Popcorn**: Air-popped popcorn is a whole grain snack that is low in calories and high in fiber. You can season it with herbs or nutritional yeast for added taste without a lot of calories.\n\n5. **Nuts and Seeds**: A small handful of almonds, walnuts, or sunflower seeds can provide healthy fats and protein. Purchase in bulk to save money.\n\n6. **Rice Cakes with Nut Butter**: Brown rice cakes spread with almond or peanut butter can be a satisfying and crunchy snack. You can also top them with banana slices or a sprinkle of cinnamon.\n\n7. **Cottage Cheese**: High in protein and versatile, cottage cheese can be eaten plain or mixed with fruits or vegetables.\n\n8. **Whole Grain Crackers**: Look for options that are high in fiber and low in added sugars. Pair with cheese or avocado for added nutrition.\n\n9. **Hard-Boiled Eggs**: A great source of protein and healthy fats, hard-boiled eggs are easy to prepare in advance and can be enjoyed on the go.\n\n10. **Edamame**: These young soybeans are high in protein and fiber. You can buy them frozen and steam them for a quick snack.\n\nThese options are not only healthy but can also be prepared in advance or are easy to grab on the go, making them ideal for snacking throughout the day.",
